<subSubSection id="4AB7D3D1FF88FFB3FF65FB97FBC4FB42" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="0212805AFF88FFB3FF65FB97FBC4FB42" blockId="25.[136,1452,373,1265]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF88FFB3FF65FB97FEFEFBEC" bold="true" box="[189,318,1093,1119]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Comments</emphasis>
:—In Marambaia, it is restricted to Shrubby 
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF88FFB3FCEFFB95FC59FBD3" box="[823,921,1095,1120]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Restinga</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF88FFB3FC09FB95FBF3FBD3" box="[977,1075,1095,1120]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Restinga</emphasis>
Forest. 
<taxonomicName id="C5ADFBD9FF88FFB3FB48FB94FA51FBD3" authorityName="Baillon" authorityYear="1879" baseAuthorityName="Candolle" baseAuthorityYear="1828" box="[1168,1425,1094,1120]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Melastomataceae" genus="Tibouchina" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="trichopoda">
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF88FFB3FB48FB94FA51FBD3" box="[1168,1425,1094,1120]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Tibouchina trichopoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinguished by leaves with 3–5 basal acrodromous veins, marginal veins not diverging from the inner ones, appressedstrigulose adaxial surface, and abaxial surface with sericeous blade and appressed-hirtellous acrodromous venation. In addition, involucral and concave bracteoles, and the filaments basally glandular-pubescent also identify this species. Additional illustrations in 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF88FFB3FE77FB04FDA4FB43" author="Cogniaux, A." box="[431,612,1238,1264]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" pagination="1 - 510" refId="ref24081" refString="Cogniaux, A. (1883 - 1888) Melastomaceae. In: Martius, C. F. P., Eichler, A. G. &amp; Urban, I. (Eds.) Flora brasiliensis 14 (3): 1 - 510, (4): 1 - 656." type="journal article" year="1883">Cogniaux (1883</bibRefCitation>
–1888), and 
<bibRefCitation id="663CFDABFF88FFB3FD29FB04FBC0FB42" author="Baumgratz, J. F. A. &amp; Souza, M. L. D. R. &amp; Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A." box="[753,1024,1238,1265]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" pagination="591 - 646" refId="ref22935" refString="Baumgratz, J. F. A., Souza, M. L. D. R., Carraca, D. C. &amp; Abbas, B. A. (2006) Melastomataceae na Reserva Biologica de Poco das Antas, Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro, Brasil: aspectos floristicos e taxonomicos. Rodriguesia 57 (3): 591 - 646." type="journal article" year="2006">
Baumgratz 
<emphasis id="30D95C48FF88FFB3FCABFB05FC6BFB43" box="[883,939,1238,1264]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">et al.</emphasis>
(2006)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
